<figureCitation box="[1285,1353,1868,1893]" captionStart="FIGURE 6" captionStartId="18.[151,250,1416,1438]" captionTargetBox="[164,1420,808,1348]" captionTargetId="figure@18.[161,1425,805,1351]" captionTargetPageId="18" captionText="FIGURE 6. Mylabris (M.) apiceguttata Pan &amp; Bologna sp. n.: A. antenna; B. elytral pattern; C. mesosternum; D. tegmen, ventral view; E. tegmen, lateral view; F. aedeagus, lateral view; G. spiculum gastrale, dorsal view. Scale bar = 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/286147/files/figure.png" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
